contentrichtext.text: '''ICV''' can stand for: * [[ICVolunteers]] / [http://fr.wikipedia.org/ICVolontaires ICVolontaires] / ICVoluntarios * Cargolux Italia, an airline using the [[ICAO airline designator]] ICV * Idle Control Valve, a device to control the idle speed of an internal combustion engine. *[[Integrity check value]] *Infantry combat vehicle, see [[Infantry fighting vehicle]] *[[Initiative for Catalonia Greens]], a political party of Catalonia. * International certificate of vaccination, see [[Carte Jaune]] *International Congress of Vexillology, see [[FIAV#International_Congresses_of_Vexillology|Fédération internationale des associations vexillologiques]] *Intracerebroventricular region of the brain *[[Ileocecal valve]] {{disambig}}
